(5\) ACCOMMODATIONS AND MODIFICATIONS) Tj
T*
(Instructional Accommodations:) Tj
T*
(- Extended time \(up to 1.5x\) for reading-heavy assignments and classroom assessments.) Tj
T*
(- Directions read aloud and checked for understanding before independent work.) Tj
T*
(- Access to graphic organizers, sentence starters, and exemplar models for writing tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Preferential seating near instruction and reduced-distraction testing location as needed.) Tj
T*
(- Chunked assignments with interim check-ins every 10-15 minutes.) Tj
T*
(Assessment Accommodations:) Tj
T*
(- Small-group setting, repeated directions, and text-to-speech for eligible district assessments.) Tj
T*
() Tj
